      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           read      fil    next
                            with no lock
                            at end
                            go to   nxt-600.
           go to     nxt-500.
       nxt-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Read next with lock                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           read      fil    next
                            at end
                            go to   nxt-600.
       nxt-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
