           go to     ktk-325.
       ktk-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Update record                                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   upd-000              thru upd-999                .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Release record                                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   rel-000              thru rel-999                .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo a Get Next                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     ktk-100.
       ktk-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Close modulo per richiamo filtri, con comunica- *
      *              * zione attributi sul filtro                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "CL"                 to   s-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msqzkk"
                                         using s                      .
           cancel    "swd/mod/prg/obj/msqzkk"                         .
           if        s-sts                not  = spaces
                     move  e-fat-err      to   f-sts
                     go to ktk-999.
       ktk-999.
